515
00:32:08,622 --> 00:32:09,691
Nastavi da se vraćaš.

516
00:32:09,862 --> 00:32:11,580
Radi ako radiš.

517
00:32:19,103 --> 00:32:20,138
Ben?

518
00:32:20,741 --> 00:32:23,302
